      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_chap15.pdf_3_2",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "Unfair and Deceptive Practices",
        "bbox": [
          0.10833333333333334,
          0.2906666666666667,
          0.4483333333333333,
          0.3413333333333333
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_chap15.pdf_3_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "An unfair and deceptive practice is an act that misleads consumers. Most states have enacted either the Uniform Deceptive Trade",
        "bbox": [
          0.1075,
          0.3433333333333333,
          0.4975,
          0.4
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_chap15.pdf_3_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Practices Act or their own similar laws. In Texas, for example, the Texas Deceptive Trade Practices Act (DTPA) was enacted to protect consumers against false, misleading, and deceptive business and insurance prac- tices, and unconscionable actions and breach of warranty. Although state laws differ, all are similar to federal law. If you believe you are the vic- tim of an unfair or deceptive practice, you might start by contacting the business with your complaint. Figure 15.1 provides an example of a complaint letter that you might send.",
        "bbox": [
          0.1075,
          0.4013333333333333,
          0.6958333333333333,
          0.5566666666666666
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_chap15.pdf_3_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Federal Consumer Protection law applies to interstate commerce. Does federal consumer protection law apply to a local farmstand business?",
        "bbox": [
          0.7233333333333334,
          0.45466666666666666,
          0.915,
          0.5533333333333333
        ],
        "order": 8
      }
    ]
  },
